Deji Onadeko, a Nigerian TV personality has revealed the horrific thing that has happened to him. Onadeko who took to his Instagram page to make the disclosure, revealed that his car has gotten burgled for the second time in just four months, a development which has left him really sad. He shared photos of his burgled vehicle on his Instagram page, lamenting to his fans. He then wrote: “Guyssss… look what I woke up to, my car got burgled again, for the second time in 4 months, “I can’t even lie, this one hit me hard, I have to start with the merry go round of police report, back and forth the mechanic, raising the money to fix it, “honestly, I’m weak and sad.” See more photos: